title: Richard II, Makers of History
creator: Jacob Abbott
description: LibriVox recording of Richard II, Makers of History, by Jacob Abbott, read by Cathy Barratt. Chronicles the life of Richard II, born in 1367 in Bordeaux, France, who later wore the crown of King of England. (Summary by Cathy Barratt) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
subject: librivox; audiobook; Richard; Makers of History; Jacob Abbott; history
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody:
Interesting history superbly read by Cathy Barratt.  I learned a lot that I had not known before, and gained a better perspective on the selectivity of chivalry.

Would recommend this for anyone interested in filling in some of the historical details that they missed in school.
Happily listening along, and while I know this is not a review - how would you quote from this work using MLA format?
